   [ Keyword Search ] KEYWORD
     * Searches terms from ALL fields in the record (AUTHOR, TITLE,
       SUBJECT, NOTES, ORDER NUMBER, etc.) or specifically selected fields
       (SUBJECT, AUTHOR, TITLE).
     * Search TIPS: Truncate search words using*; e.g., nurs* will search
       nurse, nurses, nursing, etc.
     * The fewer search words used, the broader (and sometimes better) the
       result.

   [ Browse Terms Index ] BROWSE
     * Displays specific lists of terms in the database in alphabetical
       order.You may scan and browse the list and double click on terms to
       retrieve specific images.

